descriptionHtml:
About Merino Laminates
Our market presence in over 80+ countries and our extensive product range make Merino Laminates one of the world's leading manufacturer and exporter of decorative laminates for the interiors segment.

We showcase a range of world class, premium laminates with more than 10,000 designs, textures, colours and finishes. Complementary products from the Merino Group include plywood, melamine-faced particle board & MDF board, and post-formed panels for the interiors industry.

We have committed ourselves to uphold the highest manufacturing standards, a practice that has earned all our facilities pertinent certifications that include ISO 9001, ISO 14001 and OHSAS 18001.

Founded in 1968, the Merino Group is today INR1500Cr+ group with diverse business interests which include Panel & Panel Products, Biotechnology (Agriculture & Food Processing) and Information Technology (IT). We are driven by our constant effort to maintain Economy, Excellence and Ethics in all our businesses.

About Merino Humrahi
Merino Humrahi is a specially designed loyalty programme authorised dealers & their associated carpenters & contractors.

At Merino, we recognize that all our achievements have been made possible due to the relentless commitment of our partners. Our relationship needs nurturing at every step, and through Merino Humrahi programme, we are partnering with you to excel and grow even further, A family that stays together, WIN together and achieve goals together

The Programme
Merino Humrahi, our unique Loyalty Programme aims to:
• Enhance dealer relationships with Carpenters and Contractors
• Reward Carpenters, Contractors and dealers
• Improve sales at dealer counter
Based on their association & transactions each member can earn reward points, accumulate these reward points in their Merino Humrahi account & can later redeem these against exciting rewards of their liking.

Features of Merino Humrahi App
This app will aid members to manage their Humrahi accounts at ease i.e. anytime, anywhere. Key Features of the app are as:
• Recommend member
• Record Sales
• View Account Summary & statement
• Redeem Reward
• View Profile
